data.title: Feeding America West Michigan
data.meta_description: Resources and information for people seeking help with food in West Michigan and the Upper Peninsula.
data.text:
Use this map to locate food pantries and meal programs (green apple and milk icon), upcoming Mobile Food Pantries (blue truck icon), and Gather 2 Grow sites (orange reading person icon) near you.

You can also reference the other resources under the “Get Help” tab, and can find our Mobile Pantry schedule here. Please note that locations, times, and methods of distributions are subject to change. For the most accurate information, please contact the agency directly. If you represent an agency and would like to update your listing, please contact our agency partnerships team.
